{"tid":686221,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"LG OLED 電視出事了？僅用三個月便已留烙印！","createTime":"2018-06-01T05:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T10:09:22.000Z","uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b256cc956e6b7bf0a72d53a688487150871bb3a","tid":686221,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5fD760591hFYaix8C4ehGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMxMC44NTcxNDI4NTcxNDI4Mw--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/LwHUbeqNELt_9vvsKECDaQ--~B/aD0zNzQ7dz03NzA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/pc3mag.com/2fc4949d55feb7d935bbc24c2fa4e4cf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5fD760591hFYaix8C4ehGQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMxMC44NTcxNDI4NTcxNDI4Mw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLwHUbeqNELt_9vvsKECDaQ--~B%2FaD0zNzQ7dz03NzA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fpc3mag.com%2F2fc4949d55feb7d935bbc24c2fa4e4cf&h=20384e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電視壽命理應很長，可以長時間收看不同節目，不過有時出問題並非內部硬件引起，而是外部的熒幕出現問題，最近傳出 LG OLED 電視熒幕有烙印問題，事源是放置於南韓仁川機場作展示用途的 LG OLED 電視熒幕，該電視在年初一月才安裝，用於顯示飛機班表，僅三個月後已發現熒幕有一條白線烙印。<br />\n<br />\nLG 為宣傳 2018 年款的新型電視，於是在年初與機場合作，安裝總計 40 台新機於候機室及主要大堂。在更換過程中，原先打算另一台新的 OLED 電視，但最終還是選擇 LG Super Ultra HD TV 液晶電視，被質疑就算更換一台新電視也解決不了烙印問題，而且液晶技術的關係，能確保可以更長時間沒有烙印出現。<br />\n<br />\nOLED 螢幕色域相對較廣，同時色彩也更為鮮豔，但未能長時間使用，使用過長便容易出現烙印問題，其實用於機場展示班表，既要長時間打開，且甚少轉換畫面，其實再用液晶電視也無可口非，更加實際啦！"},{"pid":"16c42fcfdf2dcfbbc3b4ccfa8d593e5bd4312e96","tid":686221,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dd8cf7efec41a38d0069cfcb7a10b96b5b6f73","tid":686221,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"其實只要以後顯示班次個格式唔變,應該無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991a75aea73772334fb2463f62bcb97e6c4032ad","tid":686221,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"乜仲有人用LG啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbe8d41201a89104f6316defcb1ffa5da954f4b","tid":686221,"uid":32665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"烙印係咁既咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1379a974abc3f6a3ee406d56997d3a7f9410b8e5","tid":686221,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"991a75aea73772334fb2463f62bcb97e6c4032ad","tid":686221,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"乜仲有人用LG啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"其實關LG咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係LED mon嘅問題嚟"},{"pid":"ddfc6b3718b07644202f3f6d03797e30f6bbfe38","tid":686221,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"烙印邊係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 篇文咩source"},{"pid":"6f25ed6625ba485019bb9040cdbea675ba18946a","tid":686221,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"手機d烙印勁到搞到我以為自己對眼出左事<br />\n睇野有殘影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94761fffb93e7ac1e7ab6ec9d3dc62011900300b","tid":686221,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"oled tv睇航班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6f62ea11aaf983e2e5042ff0ae5aa97f57a35d","tid":686221,"uid":92477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10